@startuml
title Fluxo de Relatório por Chat
actor Usuário
participant "ChatPage.jsx" as Frontend
participant "/chat/report" as API
participant "FastAPI" as Backend
participant "extract_report_data" as Extrator
participant "calculate_risk" as Calculadora

Usuário -> Frontend: envia conversa clínica
Frontend -> API: POST /chat/report
API -> Backend: chat_report(payload)
Backend -> Extrator: extract_report_data(messages)
Extrator --> Backend: dados extraídos
Backend -> Calculadora: calculate_risk(extracted)
Calculadora --> Backend: Resultado de risco
Backend --> Frontend: { resultado, paciente }
Frontend --> Usuário: exibe relatório e permite PDF
@enduml
